\"from\": 3812, \"to\": 3831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Crucially, though, the course did so much to enhance the race: lots of laps, fast and furious stuff, with packed crowds all the way around.MO On day seven, I set out on a quest to see Team GB win four golds in four sports in one day.\", \"from\": 3833, \"to\": 4067, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4018, \"end\": 4025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.0947992401130375e-15, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 3852, \"to\": 3862}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 3886, \"to\": 3894}, {\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 3896, \"to\": 3900}, {\"ngram\": \"laps\", \"from\": 3904, \"to\": 3908}, {\"ngram\": \"fast and furious stuff\", \"from\": 3910, \"to\": 3932}, {\"ngram\": \"packed crowds\", \"from\": 3939, \"to\": 3952}, {\"ngram\": \"MO\", \"from\": 3972, \"to\": 3974}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 3978, \"to\": 3981}, {\"ngram\": \"a quest\", \"from\": 4002, \"to\": 4009}, {\"ngram\": \"four golds\", \"from\": 4029, \"to\": 4039}, {\"ngram\": \"four sports\", \"from\": 4043, \"to\": 4054}, {\"ngram\": \"one day\", \"from\": 4058, \"to\": 4065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In truth, the opening gold of the day was as much a banker as was imaginable as Imogen Grant and Emily Craig romped to rowing gold.\", \"from\": 4068, \"to\": 4199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4148, \"end\": 4160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imogen_Grant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imogen Grant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imogen_Grant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imogen_Grant\"}, {\"begin\": 4165, \"end\": 4176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Craig\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emily Craig\", \"types\": 